@ExperimentalMaterial3Api
@Composable
fun InstallMYSQLScreen(navHostController: NavHostController) {
    Surface(
        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.background
    ) {
        val scrollBehavior = TopAppBarDefaults.pinnedScrollBehavior()
        Scaffold(
            topBar = {
                TopAppBar(
                    title = {
                        Text(text = "Installing MYSQL")
                    },
                    navigationIcon = {
                        IconButton(onClick = navHostController::navigateUp) {
                            Icon(
                                imageVector = Icons.Default.ArrowBackIosNew,
                                contentDescription = "Back"
                            )
                        }
                    },
                    actions = {
                        IconButton(onClick = { /*TODO*/ }) {
                            Icon(imageVector = Icons.Default.Mic, contentDescription = "ReadAloud")
                        }
                        IconButton(onClick = { /*TODO*/ }) {
                            Icon(imageVector = Icons.Default.Share, contentDescription = "Share")
                        }
                    },
                    scrollBehavior = scrollBehavior
                )
            }
        ) { paddingValues: PaddingValues ->
            LazyColumn(
                modifier = Modifier
                    .padding(16.dp)
                    .nestedScroll(scrollBehavior.nestedScrollConnection),
                contentPadding = paddingValues
            ) {
                item {
                    Text(
                        text = AnnotatedString.fromHtml(
                            "<strong>Summary</strong>: in this tutorial, you will learn how to install MySQL server and its related products on Windows using the MySQL Installer.</p><p>After the tutorial, you will have a MySQL server and its tools up and running on your system for learning and practicing.</p>"
                        ),
                        modifier = Modifier.padding(8.dp),
                        textAlign = TextAlign.Justify
                    )
                }
                item {
                    Text(
                        text = AnnotatedString.fromHtml(
                            "<p>Note that for other operating systems like Linux and Ubuntu, refer to the following tutorials:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/getting-started-with-mysql/install-mysql-centos/\">Install MySQL 8 on CentOS 7</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/getting-started-with-mysql/install-mysql-ubuntu/\">Install MySQL 8 on Ubuntu</a></li></ul><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Download MySQL Installer</strong>\n</h2><p>If you want to install MySQL on Windows, you can use the MySQL Installer. The MySQL Installer provides you with an easy-to-use wizard that helps you to install MySQL with the following main products:</p><ul><li>MySQL Server</li><li>MySQL Workbench</li><li>MySQL Shell</li><li>MySQL Documentation</li><li>All Available Connectors</li></ul><p>To download the MySQL installer, go to the following link&nbsp;<a href=\"http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/installer/\">http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/installer/</a>.&nbsp;</p><p>We’ll use the MySQL Installer 8.0.34 to install the MySQL Server and related products such as MySQL Workbench and MySQL Shell.</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Install MySQL Server &amp; related products using MySQL Installer</h2><p>To install MySQL using the MySQL installer, double-click on the MySQL Installer file and follow the steps below:</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org//wp-content/uploads/2013/05/install-mysql-step-1.png\" alt=\"Install MySQL Step 1\"&gt;</noscript><img class=\" lazyloaded\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org//wp-content/uploads/2013/05/install-mysql-step-1.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org//wp-content/uploads/2013/05/install-mysql-step-1.png\" alt=\"Install MySQL Step 1\"><br>Step 1:&nbsp;Choosing a setup type</h3><p>In this step, you need to choose the setup type that suits your use case. For tutorial purposes, you can select the last option which is <strong>Custom</strong> setup type:</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11624\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-1.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-1-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-1-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 2. Selecting products</h3><p>Since we chose the <strong>Custom </strong>setup type, the MySQL Installer displays available products for us to select to install.</p><p>We’ll install the following products:</p><ul><li><strong>MySQL Server</strong> – This is the MySQL Database Server.</li><li><strong>MySQL Workbench</strong> – This is the client tool for interacting with the MySQL Database Server via GUI.</li><li><strong>MySQL Shell</strong> – This is an interactive Javascript, Python, or SQL interface supporting development and administration for the MySQL Server.</li></ul><p>To select these products, you click the + icon on the left pane, select the product, and click the right arrow button.</p><p>Here are the paths to the selected products:</p><ul><li>MySQL Servers &gt; MySQL Server &gt; MySQL Server 8.0 &gt; MySQL Server 8.0.34 – x64</li><li>Applications &gt; MySQL Workbench &gt; MySQL Workbench 8.0 &gt; MySQL Workbench 8.0.34 – X64</li><li>Applications &gt; MySQL Shell &gt; MySQL Shell 8.0 &gt; MySQL Shell 8.0.34 – X64</li></ul><p>Once you select the products, you click the <strong>Next</strong> button to continue.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11625\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11625 lazyloaded\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-2-768x580.png 768w\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 3. Downloading the selected products</h3><p>The MySQL Installer will download the selected products from the internet. Please ensure you have an active internet connection and wait for a few minutes for the download to complete.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11626\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11626 lazyloaded\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-3-768x580.png 768w\"></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11627\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11627 lazyloaded\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-4-768x580.png 768w\"></figure><p>After the download is complete, click the <strong>Execute</strong> button to start the installation.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11628\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11628 lazyloaded\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-5-768x580.png 768w\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 4. Installing the selected products</h3><p>The MySQL Installer will install the selected products and this process may some time.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11629\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11629 lazyloaded\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-6-768x580.png 768w\"></figure><p>After the installation is complete, click the <strong>Next</strong> button to proceed to the Product Configuration.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11630\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7.png\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11630 lazyloaded\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-7-768x580.png 768w\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 5. Configuring the MySQL Server</h3><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11631\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11631\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-8-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><p>In this step, configure the MySQL Server. Choose the <strong>Development Computer</strong> for the server configuration type, leave the other options as they are, and click the <strong>Next</strong> button.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11632\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11632\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-9-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 6. Choosing an authentication method</h3><p>It’s recommended to use strong password encryption for authentication, which is the first option.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11633\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11633\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-10-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 7. Entering a password for the root account</h3><p>Enter a secure password for the root account, which has full administrative privileges.</p><p>Be sure to store it safely and use it for <a href=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/getting-started-with-mysql/connect-to-mysql-server/\">connecting to the MySQL Server</a> in the future.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11634\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11634\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-11-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 8. Configuring MySQL Server as a Windows Service</h3><p>In this step, you can configure the MySQL Server as a Windows service, specify a service name, and choose whether to start the MySQL Server during the operating system startup.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11635\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11635\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-12-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 9. Granting file permissions</h3><p>In this step, you grant permission to MySQL to access the data directory.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11636\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11636\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-13-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 10. Displaying the selected configuration</h3><p>The MySQL Installer displays a window with the configuration steps. Click the <strong>Execute</strong> button to apply the configuration.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11637\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11637\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-14-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 11. Completing configuration</h3><p>After applying the configuration, the MySQL Installer displays the following window to indicate whether the MySQL Server has been configured successfully.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11638\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11638\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-15-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><p>After completing the configuration, click the <strong>Next</strong> button to confirm and finish.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11639\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11639\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-16-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 12. Completing installation</h3><p>The MySQL Installer displays a window to notify you that the installation is complete. Click the <strong>Finish</strong> button to close the installer.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><noscript>&lt;img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11640\" srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17-768x580.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\" /&gt;</noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1178\" height=\"889\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%201178%20889%22%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload wp-image-11640\" data-srcset=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17.png 1178w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17-200x151.png 200w, https://www.mysqltutorial.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Install-MySQL-8-Step-17-768x580.png 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px\"></figure><p>In this tutorial, you have learned how to install MySQL on your Windows using the MySQL installer.</p><div class=\"helpful-block-content\" data-title=\"\"><header><div class=\"wth-question\">Was this tutorial helpful?</div><div class=\"wth-thumbs\"> <button data-post=\"2258\" data-post-url=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/getting-started-with-mysql/install-mysql/\" data-post-title=\"Install MySQL\" data-response=\"1\" class=\"wth-btn-rounded wth-yes-btn\"> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"feather feather-thumbs-up block w-full h-full\"> <path d=\"M14 9V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3l-4 9v11h11.28a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.7l1.38-9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2.3zM7 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path> </svg> <span class=\"sr-only\"> Yes </span> </button> <button data-response=\"0\" data-post=\"2258\" data-post-url=\"https://www.mysqltutorial.org/getting-started-with-mysql/install-mysql/\" data-post-title=\"Install MySQL\" class=\"wth-btn-rounded wth-no-btn\"> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"ro